snippet.title: Checkmate Showdown | Meet THE ROOK
snippet.description:
The Rook is the grappler. Powerful & built like a brick s****house, he focuses his game plan around grabs.

What he lacks in mobility he makes up for with his impressive damage output. He's extremely dangerous up close and he will smash you on the ground or in the air, so don't get too cocky.
